===Noun===
'''бочка''' (bóčka) {{f}}, бочки (bóčki) {{p}}

# [[barrel]], [[keg]]
# [[roll]] (''[[aerobatic maneuvre]]'')
# [[ancient]] Russian [[measure]] of [[liquid]]s equal to 491.96 [[liter]]s (40 [[ведро|вёдер]])
# (''[[pejorative]] [[slang]]'') [[overweight]] person

